1|"     (*) Nabis, tyrant of Sparta, conquered by the Romans under"|FALSE
1|"     Flamininus in 195 B.C.; killed 192 B.C."|FALSE
1|"     (+) Messer Giorgio Scali. This event is to be found in"|FALSE
