1|"Romans, although the Carthaginians had their own citizens for captains."|FALSE
1|"After the death of Epaminondas, Philip of Macedon was made captain of"|FALSE
1|"their soldiers by the Thebans, and after victory he took away their"|FALSE
1|"liberty."|FALSE
